(15, 15, '<center style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><h1 class=\"headings\" style=\"margin-top: 100px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: bolder; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; width: max-content; color: black; letter-spacing: 2px; position: relative;\">SIDU RIVER BRIDGE</h1></center><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; padding: 40px 85.6094px 0px; text-align: justify;\"><p class=\"para\" style=\"margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-bottom: 50px;\">The Sidu River Bridge (Siduhe Bridge, 四渡河特大桥) is a 1,222 m-long (4,009 ft) suspension bridge crossing the valley of the Sidu River near Yesanguan in Badong County of the Hubei Province of the People\'s Republic of China. The bridge was designed by CCSHCC Second Highway Consultants Company, Limited. and built at a cost of 720 million yuan (approximately US$100 million). It opened to traffic on November 15, 2009.<img src=\"https://www.amazingbridges.ml/IMAGES/Sidu%20river%20bridge.jpg\" style=\"height: 250px; width: 350px; float: right; padding: 15px;\">&nbsp;The bridge is part of the new G50 Huyu Expressway that parallels China National Highway 318, an east-west route between Shanghai and Chongqing, crossing the wide belt of mountains that separate the Sichuan Basin from the lowlands of eastern Hubei. The Yangtze River pierces the same mountain belt 50 km (31 mi) to the north, forming the famous Three Gorges. The Yiwan Railway, completed in 2010 and running parallel to the highway, has been described as China\'s most difficult to build and most expensive (per km) rail line. The bridge spans a 500-meter-deep (1,600 ft) valley of the Sidu River (a left tributary of the Qingjiang River), and superseded the Royal Gorge Bridge and the Beipan River Guanxing Highway Bridge as the highest bridge in the world until it in turn was surpassed by the Duge Bridge in 2016.<br></p><h1 id=\"hedings\" style=\"margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2.5rem; z-index: -1; position: relative; width: max-content; text-transform: uppercase;\">HISTORY</h1><p class=\"para\" style=\"margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-bottom: 50px;\"></p><div class=\"col-12\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 250px; padding-right: 30px; float: left;\"><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowhead\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-y:0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: calc(var(--bs-gutter-y) * -1); margin-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); margin-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); text-align: center; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.137); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 1px; color: black; border: 1px solid black; line-height: 33px;\"><div class=\"col-12\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 242px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y);\">History</div></div><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowdetails\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-y:0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: calc(var(--bs-gutter-y) * -1); margin-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); margin-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); text-align: left;\"><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colleft\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557);\">Built In:</div><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colright\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) black rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557); border-image: initial;\">2005</div></div><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowhead\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-y:0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: calc(var(--bs-gutter-y) * -1); margin-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); margin-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); text-align: center; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.137); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 1px; color: black; border: 1px solid black; line-height: 33px;\"><div class=\"col-12\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 242px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y);\">Measurement</div></div><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowdetails\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-y:0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: calc(var(--bs-gutter-y) * -1); margin-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); margin-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); text-align: left;\"><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colleft\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557);\">Length:</div><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colright\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) black rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557); border-image: initial;\">1,222 m</div></div><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowdetails\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-y:0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: calc(var(--bs-gutter-y) * -1); margin-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); margin-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); text-align: left;\"><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colleft\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557);\">Width:</div><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colright\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) black rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557); border-image: initial;\">24 m</div></div><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowdetails\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-y:0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: calc(var(--bs-gutter-y) * -1); margin-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); margin-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * -0.5); text-align: left;\"><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colleft\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557);\">Height:</div><div class=\"col-6\" id=\"colright\" style=\"flex: 0 0 auto; width: 122px; max-width: 100%; padding-right: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); padding-left: calc(var(--bs-gutter-x) * 0.5); margin-top: var(--bs-gutter-y); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) black rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557); border-image: initial;\">496 m</div></div><div class=\"row\" id=\"rowhead\" style=\"--bs-gutter-x:1.5rem; --bs-gutter-